Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total resolution time of Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Average time it takes Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION after Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time it takes Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to be followed by Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Minimum time between Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and next Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION in cases where the declaration is resubmitted
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time for all instances of Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to be resolved or followed by another activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and the end of the case

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION and Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR in cases where the declaration is eventually approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Minimum time it takes for a case to be resubmitted after Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to Request Payment in cases where payment is still requested
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time from Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to Payment Handled for cases that are eventually paid
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time for Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION to be followed by Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER in cases where budget owner's approval is required
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
